 Excel Options phía dưới. Trong Excel 2003, chọn Options từ danh mục Tools.\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv align=\"justify\" style=\"background-color: white; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18.1875px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv align=\"justify\" style=\"background-color: white; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18.1875px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"\u003E- Trong Panel bên trái, chọn mục Save. Với Excel 2003, chọn thẻ\u0026nbsp;General\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv align=\"justify\" style=\"background-color: white; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18.1875px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv align=\"justify\" style=\"background-color: white; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18.1875px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"\u003E- Trong ô nhập sau dòng chữ Default File Location, bạn hãy gõ đường dẫn tới thư mục mà mình muốn lưu file hoặc nhấn\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/blogger.g?blogID=239657226724573368\" id=\"ch-link-8\" rel=\"how do i directed firefox browser to open pdf file|8\" style=\"border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 129, 189) !important; border-bottom-style: dotted !important; border-bottom-width: 1px !important; color: rgb(0, 129, 189) !important; text-decoration: none !important;\"\u003EBrowser\u003C\/a\u003E\u0026nbsp;để duyệt chọn. Sau cùng nhấn OK.\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv align=\"justify\" style=\"background-color: white; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 18.1875px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\"\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http:\/\/images.xhtt.vn\/Images\/Uploaded\/Share\/2012\/08\/20120818092345953\/image003.png\" style=\"background-image: url(http:\/\/thuthuatso.com\/wp-content\/themes\/thuthuatso\/images\/imgbg.jpg); background-position: 50% 100%; background-repeat: repeat